00:01:59,587 --> 00:02:03,220
昨天 像是要证明自己的特立独行
<i>Yesterday, as if to confirm the general opinion of her oddity,</i>

31
00:02:03,259 --> 00:02:04,442
她声称她会
<i>she declared that she would</i>

32
00:02:04,479 --> 00:02:08,051
自己驾船穿过湖泊去教堂
<i>sail herself to church across the lake.</i>

33
00:02:27,200 --> 00:02:32,960

34
00:02:46,274 --> 00:02:49,052
在旅馆的马车上 大家还纷纷猜测着
<i>There was much speculation in the hotel carriage</i>

35
00:02:49,089 --> 00:02:52,632
在前往湖边那座 精致的小礼拜堂的路上
<i>as we traveled towards the charming little lakeside chapel</i>

36
00:02:52,669 --> 00:02:54,182
谈论Frances女士是否
<i>about whether Lady Frances</i>

37
00:02:54,220 --> 00:02:56,310
能像她所说的那么能干
<i>would be as good as her word.</i>

38
00:02:56,349 --> 00:02:58,156
