<i>will be lifted by her brother's visit</i>

147
00:09:35,501 --> 00:09:36,732
不要再压抑
<i>for she remains subdued</i>

148
00:09:36,770 --> 00:09:40,024
昨天与那陌生人的偶遇而产生的心情
<i>from yesterday's strange encounter.</i>

149
00:09:42,073 --> 00:09:43,999
他是谁  福尔摩斯
<i>Who is he, Holmes?</i>

150
00:09:44,036 --> 00:09:47,949
为什么他不希望自己被认出
<i>Why does he not wish to make himself known?</i>

151
00:09:51,488 --> 00:09:54,077
到底是为什么
Why indeed?

152
00:10:15,629 --> 00:10:18,561
华生  你真有份好心肠
Watson, you're a brick.

153
00:10:19,484 --> 00:10:21,630
我来到这里  Fanny 是想知道你的近况
I came here, Fanny, to see how you were,

154
00:10:21,668 --> 00:10:22,806
而不是被说教
not to be lectured.

155
